WEBVTT

00:00:07.825 --> 00:00:11.562
♪I found a faint light
in the fading dusk♪

00:00:11.812 --> 00:00:15.130
♪And met your steady gaze♪

00:00:15.412 --> 00:00:23.912
♪One knowing glance,
and side by side we walk on♪

00:00:24.675 --> 00:00:27.062
♪Longing finds no place to rest♪

00:00:27.162 --> 00:00:29.200
♪Through drifting wind and rain♪

00:00:29.312 --> 00:00:32.500
♪You are the prayer within my hands♪

00:00:32.800 --> 00:00:40.340
♪A single second frozen,
tears in focus, my heart already knows♪

00:00:40.425 --> 00:00:42.837
♪We made a promise long ago♪

00:00:42.887 --> 00:00:44.737
♪For all our days to come♪

00:00:44.887 --> 00:00:48.400
♪You are the fate I cannot outrun♪

00:00:48.550 --> 00:00:53.825
♪How much must I let go
to trade for one moment?♪

00:00:53.937 --> 00:00:56.237
♪Holding you close♪

00:00:56.737 --> 00:00:58.737
♪Would that be enough?♪

00:00:58.875 --> 00:00:59.659
=Echoes of Love=

00:00:59.660 --> 00:01:01.474
(Adapted from the signed screenplay
Echoes of Love on Migu Reading)

00:01:01.712 --> 00:01:03.425
=Episode 3=

00:01:05.975 --> 00:01:08.375
(Jiang Bishui, Luo Yunchuan,
Ru Yu, He Yuyan)

00:01:08.680 --> 00:01:09.760
Over the years,

00:01:09.760 --> 00:01:11.159
dozens of courtesans have vanished

00:01:11.400 --> 00:01:12.439
without a trace.

00:01:13.162 --> 00:01:14.362
I investigated in secret

00:01:14.480 --> 00:01:15.879
and found that most of them

00:01:15.879 --> 00:01:17.280
were from Huanyue House.

00:01:17.959 --> 00:01:19.159
During today's interrogation,

00:01:19.640 --> 00:01:21.319
we learned of the Shengtang Guild..

00:01:21.879 --> 00:01:23.439
They deal in trafficking courtesans.

00:01:24.560 --> 00:01:26.079
They're hunting you

00:01:26.760 --> 00:01:28.319
because you're the only one

00:01:28.319 --> 00:01:29.799
who ever escaped them.

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:38.400
(Jiang Bishui, Luo Yunchuan, Ru Yu, He Yuyan)
Taoli. Yunxia. Chilan.

00:01:38.719 --> 00:01:39.560
Zhaodi.

00:01:41.359 --> 00:01:42.000
So

00:01:42.799 --> 00:01:44.239
I wasn't the only victim.

00:01:45.900 --> 00:01:47.787
Huanyue House is about
to host the Flower Festival.

00:01:48.319 --> 00:01:49.079
A painter

00:01:49.280 --> 00:01:51.680
from the Shengtang Guild will attend
to select new courtesans.

00:01:52.480 --> 00:01:53.879
The begonia tattoo on their arms

00:01:53.879 --> 00:01:54.959
is their mark.

00:01:55.480 --> 00:01:56.637
I'll be undercover.

00:01:57.000 --> 00:01:58.362
When the time comes,

00:01:58.480 --> 00:01:59.680
we'll capture the painter.

00:02:01.280 --> 00:02:02.840
Once this mission is over,

00:02:03.280 --> 00:02:04.519
I'll see you out of the capital.

00:02:05.760 --> 00:02:07.000
(Begonia flower...)

00:02:07.799 --> 00:02:09.560
All right. I understand.

00:02:11.037 --> 00:02:11.836
Official Gu.

00:02:13.412 --> 00:02:14.252
This time,

00:02:14.560 --> 00:02:16.639
I'll do everything I can
to help you solve the case.

00:02:18.039 --> 00:02:19.360
Not just for myself.

00:02:25.520 --> 00:02:26.439
Zhou Zihua,

00:02:26.960 --> 00:02:28.337
you've followed me for years.

00:02:28.759 --> 00:02:31.287
And you can't even handle
a mere courtesan?

00:02:31.439 --> 00:02:32.599
Or is it

00:02:32.599 --> 00:02:34.325
that your loyalties have shifted?

00:02:35.280 --> 00:02:36.520
It was Gu Chengye.

00:02:36.850 --> 00:02:37.931
He interfered.

00:02:40.120 --> 00:02:41.560
Him again.

00:02:45.039 --> 00:02:47.520
The Flower Festival is next month.

00:02:47.520 --> 00:02:49.100
As for the courtesan queen selection,

00:02:49.280 --> 00:02:51.120
there must be no mistakes.

00:02:51.319 --> 00:02:52.240
Otherwise,

00:02:52.639 --> 00:02:55.400
I'll make your face bloom
with begonia flowers.

00:02:55.759 --> 00:02:57.237
So you'll never forget

00:02:57.960 --> 00:02:59.639
who you belong to.

00:03:00.319 --> 00:03:01.439
Yes.

00:03:25.840 --> 00:03:28.319
(If Liu Ruyan is the only survivor,)

00:03:28.919 --> 00:03:30.159
(and Huanyue House)

00:03:30.159 --> 00:03:31.919
(is working
with the Shengtang Guild,)

00:03:32.960 --> 00:03:35.360
(then why did Liu Ruyan
return before she died?)

00:03:39.587 --> 00:03:42.087
(Ancestral Virtue and Merit)

00:03:56.800 --> 00:04:01.387
(Spirit Tablet of the Gu Clan)

00:04:01.960 --> 00:04:03.520
Sir, that was a brilliant move.

00:04:04.479 --> 00:04:05.800
You gave her no real help,

00:04:06.439 --> 00:04:07.840
yet told her the truth.

00:04:08.520 --> 00:04:09.240
That way,

00:04:09.240 --> 00:04:12.439
she had no choice but to risk herself
and draw out the mastermind for you.

00:04:13.520 --> 00:04:15.080
I deliberately refused to work with her,

00:04:15.639 --> 00:04:17.399
while leaving obvious flaws.

00:04:18.079 --> 00:04:19.959
So she would press forward step by step,

00:04:20.550 --> 00:04:22.650
thinking it was all her own doing.

00:04:24.262 --> 00:04:24.661
Sir,

00:04:24.937 --> 00:04:26.500
Miss Song has been compromised.

00:04:30.600 --> 00:04:32.279
Look at my face.

00:04:33.040 --> 00:04:34.862
This is all thanks to you.

00:04:37.125 --> 00:04:38.680
Do you know how much effort

00:04:38.680 --> 00:04:40.120
I put into this face?

00:04:40.120 --> 00:04:41.850
And now it's ruined because of you.

00:04:42.720 --> 00:04:44.439
I groomed you with care.

00:04:44.759 --> 00:04:46.360
I raised you
to become courtesan queen.

00:04:46.360 --> 00:04:48.439
And you dared collude
with Gu Chengye behind my back.

00:04:48.439 --> 00:04:49.920
(He's with the Shengtang Guild too?)

00:04:50.000 --> 00:04:51.120
Song Zhiyun.

00:04:51.800 --> 00:04:52.920
Today

00:04:53.519 --> 00:04:55.360
is the day you die.

00:04:55.759 --> 00:04:57.560
(I can't. I have to survive.)

00:04:59.839 --> 00:05:00.399
Wait.

00:05:01.199 --> 00:05:01.959
Master Zhou.

00:05:04.040 --> 00:05:04.839
Master Zhou.

00:05:05.759 --> 00:05:06.600
Your face...

00:05:07.160 --> 00:05:07.839
I can fix it.

00:05:08.160 --> 00:05:09.720
I can restore it.

00:05:10.120 --> 00:05:12.273
I can even make you
more beautiful than before.

00:05:14.120 --> 00:05:16.360
Please. Just trust me this once.

00:05:45.480 --> 00:05:46.079
Master Zhou,

00:05:46.480 --> 00:05:48.160
that begonia on your hand

00:05:48.160 --> 00:05:49.160
is rather plain.

00:05:49.560 --> 00:05:50.160
Why not

00:05:50.680 --> 00:05:52.439
let me add a touch of color?

00:06:30.837 --> 00:06:31.875
No.

00:06:32.639 --> 00:06:33.480
No!

00:06:36.279 --> 00:06:39.720
The Shengtang Guild cleaned up
quite a mess for you,

00:06:39.720 --> 00:06:41.839
so you could return to Huanyue House.

00:06:42.560 --> 00:06:44.560
It's only fair you repay the favor.

00:06:44.959 --> 00:06:45.920
From now on,

00:06:45.920 --> 00:06:47.925
you'll serve as the boss.

00:07:01.040 --> 00:07:02.079
How beautiful.

00:07:05.199 --> 00:07:06.759
If you're willing to keep me,

00:07:06.759 --> 00:07:08.720
I can do your makeup every day

00:07:08.720 --> 00:07:10.837
and make you the most beautiful in the world.

00:07:16.360 --> 00:07:17.480
You are

00:07:18.360 --> 00:07:20.240
my most perfect creation.

00:07:21.519 --> 00:07:23.160
How could I bear to kill you?

00:07:26.240 --> 00:07:27.720
But you're far too disobedient.

00:07:28.162 --> 00:07:29.680
You've caused a great deal of trouble.

00:07:30.319 --> 00:07:32.160
You need to be taught some discipline.

00:07:33.279 --> 00:07:34.079
Du Jinchun.

00:07:34.079 --> 00:07:34.959
I'm here.

00:07:37.959 --> 00:07:39.787
Master Zhou?

00:07:40.319 --> 00:07:42.079
Let me go.

00:07:43.519 --> 00:07:44.480
Master Zhou!

00:07:44.480 --> 00:07:46.439
The women of Huanyue House

00:07:46.439 --> 00:07:48.360
have never soiled
their hands with labor.

00:07:48.959 --> 00:07:50.920
Their nails are pink as the dawn.

00:07:51.319 --> 00:07:52.800
This delicate bridal adornment

00:07:53.680 --> 00:07:55.680
is unique to Huanyue House.

00:07:56.160 --> 00:07:57.240
It's called

00:07:57.680 --> 00:07:59.120
A Touch of Red.

00:08:02.399 --> 00:08:03.240
Master Zhou!

00:08:03.720 --> 00:08:04.759
Let me go!

00:08:08.160 --> 00:08:09.160
Let me go!

00:08:10.519 --> 00:08:12.759
From now on, I'll say a line,

00:08:13.120 --> 00:08:14.279
and you repeat it.

00:08:14.600 --> 00:08:15.920
"Humility above all."

00:08:23.639 --> 00:08:24.560
(So that means...)

00:08:25.439 --> 00:08:27.000
(Liu Ruyan did nothing at all.)

00:08:27.639 --> 00:08:28.439
(It was)

00:08:28.439 --> 00:08:30.187
(all slander and a setup against her.)

00:08:30.720 --> 00:08:32.559
(Why would you do this to Liu Ruyan?)

00:08:32.759 --> 00:08:34.320
(Just one careless sentence,)

00:08:34.840 --> 00:08:37.240
(and she was condemned
as a wanton harlot.)

00:08:37.559 --> 00:08:39.712
(No. I will clear her name.)

00:08:42.812 --> 00:08:43.373
Sir,

00:08:44.720 --> 00:08:45.720
leave her one hand

00:08:46.279 --> 00:08:47.360
so she can do your makeup.

00:08:49.159 --> 00:08:50.559
Since you're fond of her,

00:08:51.840 --> 00:08:52.799
so be it.

00:08:57.759 --> 00:08:59.475
Sir, the Commander has arrived.

00:08:59.679 --> 00:09:01.320
He's here to shut down Huanyue House.

00:09:04.679 --> 00:09:05.919
Go deal with him.

00:09:06.712 --> 00:09:07.512
Yes, sir.

00:09:10.159 --> 00:09:11.320
And you,

00:09:11.799 --> 00:09:12.879
Song Zhiyun.

00:09:13.800 --> 00:09:14.759
You know

00:09:14.812 --> 00:09:16.412
what should be said

00:09:16.500 --> 00:09:18.140
and what shouldn't, don't you?

00:09:26.559 --> 00:09:27.360
Gu Chengye...

00:09:39.919 --> 00:09:40.799
Official Gu,

00:09:42.537 --> 00:09:43.657
paying a visit so late?

00:09:43.987 --> 00:09:45.506
What brings you here?

00:09:45.960 --> 00:09:47.039
These days,

00:09:48.159 --> 00:09:50.100
even one of Zhou Zihua's dogs

00:09:50.399 --> 00:09:51.799
can speak like a man.

00:09:53.120 --> 00:09:55.120
Three years ago, you were a nobody.

00:09:55.720 --> 00:09:58.360
Now you're second-in-command
at Huanyue House.

00:09:58.700 --> 00:10:00.080
Looks like

00:10:01.200 --> 00:10:03.440
you've done
plenty of dirty work for him.